fields.name: NANSLS Bluetooth Headset
fields.description:
NANSLS headset Bluetooth phone with Bluetooth V5.3 can achieve more stable pairing and connect with devices within 10 meters (barrier-free) for a long time. Compatible with HiFi stereo music, Siri and various iOS and Android systems, you can enjoy the convenience of headphones anytime, anywhere.

The wireless headset has a built-in 100mAh large capacity battery, the maximum usage time of the hands-free Bluetooth earphone for hands-free calls is 9-10 hours, the ultra-long standby time is 6.5 days. The 400mAh charging case is compact, displays the remaining power percentage for charging, and can support 4 charges.

fields.name: Kuizil Smartwatch Men Women with Phone Function
fields.description:
1.91'' touchscreen and customizable watch face: The smartwatch 1.9" HD touchscreen, equipped with four adjustable brightness levels, you can see the data clearly even in direct sunlight. The "Gloryfit" app also offers over 100 customizable watch face backgrounds to choose from or upload your favorite picture to personalize your stopwatch and show your unique style.


Bluetooth call and message reminder: After connecting to the phone via Bluetooth, you can receive or make calls directly from the smart watch. Use the keypad to dial and answer or end calls anytime, anywhere. This fitness watch for women also supports notifications for messages and social media (WhatsApp, Twitter, Facebook, Instagram, etc.)

fields.name: Soundcore Boom 2 Plus outdoor speaker
fields.description:
Booming bass with 140W max: Feel the bass in every song with two woofers for deep and clear tones. Thanks to BassUp 2.0, the maximum power increases from 100W to an incredible 140W - that's 160% more than the 1st generation of BassUp.

2+2 stereo sound: Two 50W woofers and two 20W tweeters provide deep bass and crystal clear highs. The intelligent crossover technology perfectly matches them to create the right balance and an intense audio experience.

fields.name: INIU Magsafe Power Bank, 10000mAh 20W Magnetic External Battery
fields.description: INIU Market's Thinnest 0.5-inch 10000mAh PowerPaw: Its slim and lightweight design effortlessly slips into your pocket or bag, ensuring instant on-the-go charging anywhere you need. This power bank features a USB-C port for both input and output, supporting Type-C devices' fast charging or recharging of the power bank itself. What sets it apart is its ability to charge 3 devices at once, no more carrying multiple chargers with you. The robust 10,000mAh capacity ensures uninterrupted power for all your devices throughout the day.

fields.name: Sonos Arc Soundbar
fields.description:
Home cinema sound: with the Sonos Arc Smart Sound Bar, you can set up a home cinema and enjoy truly impressive sound thanks to Dolby Atmos technology and 11 speakers that surround you with remarkable depth.

COMPACT DESIGN The compact size and slim design of the Sonos Arc TV Soundbar make it look like a decorative element, and its eleven speakers deliver a wide sound field with high-quality bass.

Technology: The Sonos Arc is equipped with 11 speakers, including 8 elliptical woofers for deep bass and balanced mids, as well as 3 tweeters for Dolby Atmos sound effects. Optimize the sound of your Sonos Arc with Trueplay and enjoy multi-dimensional, deep and nuanced sound.

fields.name: Beamer 4K Supports Full HD 1080P
fields.description: 2.4+5G WIFI and Bluetooth 5.2 projector: 4K projector with WIFI and Bluetooth, with built-in improved speaker, you can enjoy a cinematic audio-visual experience without connecting external speakers. This portable projector also integrates Bluetooth 5.2 technology to make audio synchronization faster and more stable. With this Bluetooth projector, you can wirelessly connect your ideal Bluetooth speakers or headphones at any time to get even more wonderful sound.

fields.name: LG OLED42C47LA TV 42 Inch
fields.description:
Discover a new dimension of viewing with the LG OLED evo C4 series. The top-class picture quality combined with innovative design gives you an incomparable TV experience. Immerse yourself in vivid colors, deep blacks and breathtaking contrasts.

Self-luminous pixels

Thanks to the self-illuminating pixels, you can experience the deepest blacks, vivid colors and breathtaking contrasts, without any backlighting. This is because each pixel generates its own light, which enables precise control and creates an incomparable viewing experience. With the LG OLED evo C series, you can enjoy films, series and games in their true brilliance, without annoying halos and halo effects.

Only an α processor makes an OLED so lively

The α9 Gen7 4K AI processor is the heart of the new LG OLED C4 series and offers outstanding performance for image and sound processing, optimizing colors and details in a remarkable way.

fields.name: Samsung Galaxy Tab S9 FE Wi-Fi 10.9” 128GB Android Tablet
fields.description: Meet Galaxy Tab S9 FE Wi-Fi, a powerful tablet that makes adventure more fun. This perfect intro to tablets boasts a powerful processor, long-lasting battery and dynamic screen. You’ll have plenty of room on your 10.9" screen*, explore your creativity with the included S Pen or enjoy your entertainment. Tab S9 FE Wi-Fi has enhanced durability** and is one of the only water- and dust-resistant tablets on the market**********. *Measured diagonally, the Galaxy Tab S9 FE screen size is 10.9" in the full rectangle and 10.8" accounting for the rounded corners. Actual viewable area is less due to the rounded corners. **Consistent with IP68 rating, water resistant in up to 5 feet of water for up to 30 minutes. Rinse residue / dry after wet. ***Based on local, 720p resolution video playback, default video player (full screen), 162 nit brightness, earbud volume 7, Wi-Fi and mobile network off. Results vary with settings, usage and other factors. ****Requires 45W wall charger (sold separately). Use only Samsung-approved charger and USB-C cable. To avoid injury or damage to your device, do not use incompatible, worn or damaged batteries, chargers or cables. *****Portion of storage / memory occupied by existing content. ******MicroSD card sold separately. *******Only in 16:9 FHD resolution. ********Quick Share between Galaxy devices available with the following OS: smartphones and tablets with Android OS version 10.0 (Q) and One UI 2.1 or above, PCs running Windows 10 or later. Requires Samsung account and Wi-Fi and Bluetooth connection. Quick Share to iOS and Android devices available by sending shared link: individual files shared cannot exceed 3GB (for a total of 5GB per day) and link will expire after two days; requires a Samsung account and internet connection. *********Requires a Galaxy phone to have One UI 2.5 or later. Devices must be logged in to the same Samsung account and be on the same Wi-Fi network. **********Compared to Galaxy Tab S7 FE.

fields.name: ASUS ROG Strix G16 (2024) Gaming Laptop
fields.description: Raise your game and carry your squad with the new ROG Strix G16, a powerful gaming laptop that features Windows 11, a 13th Gen Intel Core processor, and an NVIDIA® GeForce RTX™ 40 Series Laptop GPU. With DDR5-4800MHz memory and PCIe Gen4 SSD, this laptop is designed to provide lightning-fast performance and minimize loading times. The ROG Intelligent Cooling system with upgraded liquid metal on the CPU and Tri-Fan Technology, ensures that the laptop can handle the power it can deliver. The FHD Display guarantees a premium visual experience, and the MUX Switch with Advanced Optimus optimizes both gaming performance and battery life. The laptop's design is inspired by cyberpunk aesthetics and graffiti accents, and features unique elements such as a dot matrix design on the lid and cross-hatched vents.

fields.name: DJI Mini 4K, Drone with 4K UHD Camera
fields.description: DJI Mini 4K offers an incredible way to capture the world from above in 4K. Weighing less than 249 grams makes DJI Mini 4K a great companion on any outing. It's also easy to use and boasts a 31-min max flight time, a 10km (6.2137 miles) max transmission range, incredible 4K footage, and much more.

fields.name: PlayStation 5
fields.description: (PlayStation 5) The latest Sony PlayStation introduced in November 2020. Powered by an eight-core AMD Zen 2 CPU and custom AMD Radeon GPU, the PS5 is offered in two models: with and without a 4K Blu-ray drive. Supporting a 120Hz video refresh, the PS5 is considerably more powerful than the PS4 and PS4 Pro.

fields.name: G PRO X Superlight Wireless Gaming Mouse
fields.description:
The brand new Logitech G Pro Wireless X now comes with a new sensor and lower weight! Achieve higher performance while retaining the feel of the previous Logitech G Pro. Designed with the world's leading pros to engineer the world's best competetive gaming mouse.

With hyper-minimal redesign, Pro X is Logitech's lightest and fastest mouse ever weighing in at under 63 grams. Almost 25% lighter than it's predecessor. Also with Lightspeed, the next-gen, pro-grade wireless technology that has even more responsive connectivity. The finishing touch are the PTFE Feet that gives an incredibly smooth glide.

fields.name: Alexa
fields.description: Alexa is Amazon's cloud-based voice service available on more than 100 million devices from Amazon and third-party device manufacturers. With Alexa, you can build natural voice experiences that offer customers a more intuitive way to interact with the technology they use every day.

fields.name: Canon EOS 80D
fields.description: The Canon EOS 80D features an all-new 24.2MP APS-C CMOS sensor, 45-point all cross-type autofocus system, and the company's DIGIC 6 processor. When using live view or recording video users can take advantage of the 80D's Dual Pixel CMOS AF for fast and smooth autofocus.

fields.name: AirPods (2nd generation)
fields.description: With plenty of talk and listen time, voice-activated Siri access, and an available wireless charging case, AirPods deliver an incredible wireless headphone experience. Simply take them out and they're ready to use with all your devices.

fields.name: iPhone 15 Pro
fields.description: iPhone 15 Pro is the first iPhone to feature an aerospace‑grade titanium design, using the same alloy that spacecraft use for missions to Mars. Titanium has one of the best strength‑to‑weight ratios of any metal, making these our lightest Pro models ever. You'll notice the difference the moment you pick one up.
